snippet.title: F3 Trailer | Super Mario Maker for TI-Nspire [nSMM]
snippet.description:
Note: the game footage is recorded in an emulator (student software) and runs at about ~75% speed on the handheld. 

Download here!: https://tiplanet.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=17&t=25825
Join the nSMM Discord server: https://discord.gg/yadDQBwMyc

GitHub (source code): https://github.com/onlypuppy7/nSMM/tree/main/src
----------------------------
Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q4qgeLCP7AA
----------------------------
